about.summary: Genealogical data analysis including descriptive statistics (e.g., kinship and inbreeding coefficients) and gene-dropping simulations.

name: r-genlib
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.0.8" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-genlib
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/GENLIB_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/GENLIB/GENLIB_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6a1a787d64d85a16000e29834de9f8cf1a58a618a11cd0e71ac44360de89c69a

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 1
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}            # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}      # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-matrix
    - r-rcpp >=0.9.10
    - r-bootstrap
    - r-doparallel
    - r-foreach
    - r-kinship2
    - r-lattice
    - r-quadprog
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-matrix
    - r-rcpp >=0.9.10
    - r-bootstrap
    - r-doparallel
    - r-foreach
    - r-kinship2
    - r-lattice
    - r-quadprog

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('GENLIB')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('GENLIB')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=GENLIB
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: Genealogical data analysis including descriptive statistics (e.g., kinship and inbreeding coefficients) and gene-dropping simulations.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
